$ Oracle: dbms_sql.define_column

`dbms_sql.define_column` is needed in queries (`select` statements) for each selected column.

sa:
   Use → development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/dbms/sql/describe_columns[`describe_columns`] to determine column names and → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/data-types[data types].

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/dbms/sql[`dbms_sql`]
